Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:10.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been since I last stepped on this soil?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:19.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...let people have a peaceful life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:07.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrona...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:11.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's alright.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:21.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how things are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:25.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning the Devil Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:36.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we let her attend school so we could keep an eye on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:40.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I hope Shinigami-sama can make the final decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.64,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so... Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:47.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:52.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there {\i1}is{\i0} something that's sort of mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Something mysterious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That Devil Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably ate a considerable amount of human souls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:04.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she should be progressing into a Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that this isn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure of the reason myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:16.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there was a purifying effect, for some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Sid-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not entirely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:26.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Devil Sword, in truth, should have known what she was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:31.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she is only a child who was instructed by a witch,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:37.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and even considering her background history, I think an impartial decision should be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, so let it be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble, Death Scythes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Preventing Papa's Reassignment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's {\i1}not{\i0} fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Shinigami-sama tell us to restrain ourselves to allow our wounds to heal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:09.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You know... If you always choose to stay home,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...mushrooms will grow on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,To place that will be a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sid-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:36.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...including Spirit-kun, what's the status on the\N gathering of the eight Death Scythes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:37.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Justin seems to have just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With him, and the two that arrived earlier, that makes four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, then...{\alpha&HFF&} what happened to the other four?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, then... what happened to the other four?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:52.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The representatives in Europe and in West Asia are on missions, so they couldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What about South America's representative, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a barking dog, so we can't communicate with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And Africa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Blocked our contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:13.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least half of them assembled, isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this! Hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:27.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I shouldn't be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kishin resurrected, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:38.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Can there be anything more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa, you're still young, so you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:47.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to marry and immediately retire, but I'm still single.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:55.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely commit myself to them, but, in the end, we always break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:06:00.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,When men think of commitment, they feel pressured and want to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand the power of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:12.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie-senpai, you don't understand the power of your punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:20.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, the idea that marriage is a woman's happiness is outdated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... {\alpha&HFF&}going to marry the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... going to marry the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:38.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see? The toilet will accept anything I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my ideal companion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:47.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a women's toilet, but doesn't it annoy you that the seat is up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can deal with something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good. If I don't stop Marie-san...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:58.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There will be times when even it won't handle the pressure and won't be able to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It might hide from you, Marie-san, and even leak behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How indecent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You cheating bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go to where Shinigami-sama is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of the Crushing Weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still very capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... We have to go to where Shinigami-sama is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Stein,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:48.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...why do you think Shinigami-sama wants to gather the other Death Scythes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:53.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Kishin was revived, he probably wants to plan some counter-measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:57.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong. He definitely wants to relocate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a demotion, a demotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:07.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't leave Shinigami's side, he could have used me to stop the Kishin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're trying to score some points by polishing the candle stands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I'm desperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My ex-wife already has Maka's acknowledgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:27.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If the distance between us gets any bigger, she won't feel like Papa exists at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She already feels that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:35.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be desperate since you rolled up your tuxedo sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to roll them up even further by 10 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:38.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Stein-san. Marie-san's first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:49.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:49.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She came!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of Counsel Chairmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She was pretty annoying back then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I wanted to cut up a random passerby, she would fuss about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the Kishin's resurrection your fault, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, stop that! Don't say that in front of Shinigami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:17.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just honestly say what I think is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you would immediately retire after becoming a Death Scythe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:30.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop murmuring amongst yourselves. Shinigami-sama's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Face forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:44.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you say anything to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:50.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No... that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your earphones off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:03.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Justin, am in your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! And thank you for journeying all the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:17.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think everyone knows the reason why I gathered you all in Shibusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't transfer me!{\alpha&HFF&} Don't transfer me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't transfer me! Don't transfer me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kishin Asura's resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to have a discussion on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:36.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Asura is completely insane, he's still a coward,\Nso I don't think he will be active for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:41.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the urgent matter is not to track Asura's movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:48.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...but rather to plan a counter-measure for the Wavelength of Madness that Asura spreads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:52.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein-kun, please explain the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:59.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wavelength of Madness... Is it right to think of it as Asura's soul wavelength?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right. But this wavelength is on the level of a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What effect does this Wavelength of Madness have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:11.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Every human has a bit of madness within himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:21.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Asura's Wavelength of Madness forces out the madness that resides within a human's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Madness is contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:31.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment that Asura resurrected, I felt it strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The spreading of madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're saying anyone can be affected?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:41.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:47.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that people like Justin-kun have a lower chance of being affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:56.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I don't think there would be an outbreak of madness among ordinary humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,On evil people, they will power up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:07.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at someone in the face while saying that it's unpleasant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:08.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me want to cut you up all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:09.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:15.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wavelength of Madness also causes sleeping witches to awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't just affect people either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:21.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Natural catastrophes, abnormal weather and any terror you can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So dormant enemies will start to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:31.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation became like this because of the mistakes of these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami-sama, how do you intend to correct this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't transfer me! Anything but that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:46.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was thinking of doing some reassignments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:50.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy life with my child...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it anymore...{\alpha&HFF&} I can't see the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it anymore... I can't see the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:07.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I tell Maka? I don't want to see Maka's sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:12.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit-kun will continue to be my Weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy like me? Is that okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:21.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the Death Scythes, only you can truly be called a Death Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more proud of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:26.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God, such benevolent words!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:32.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, though you were Stein-kun's Temporary Weapon and traveled freely,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...from now on, try your best not to leave Shibusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:46.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, to strengthen Shibusen, I want to have another Death Scythe remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:52.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie-chan, I want you to be Stein-kun's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:14:00.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait! I don't feel like working!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:04.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose to be the representative of Oceania because I knew how peaceful it is working there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:09.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If I work in Shibusen, I'll become so busy I'll never get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the type of person that becomes enthusiastic after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:15.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami-sama, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:25.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Azusa-chan, please use your broad vision to track down Asura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:29.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, please take up the role of Oceania's representative by replacing Marie-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:30.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Justin-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Justin-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:46.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Justin will stay on reserve!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:50.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Shibusen must change a bit from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:54.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...try to be happy even if you're angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, you're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait a moment, Spirit-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Number one: Marie Mjolnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I punch Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Number two: Marie Mjolnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I cry because I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Number three: Marie Mjolnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I face forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Number four: Marie Mjolnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I unclog the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Number five: Marie Mjolnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I marry the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Number six: Marie Mjolnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I prevent the toilet from cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Number seven: Marie Mjolnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I punch Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's play basketball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Maka! Come play basketball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:02.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Didn't you say that I could sit out and read?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I tagged along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:14.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice, because suddenly Liz didn't want to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:17.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the rules of basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:18.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, hold your hair down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the teams look fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid-kun, why didn't Liz come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she didn't want to break a nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just playing basketball is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a penalty game for the captain of the losing team?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's fine by me. I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:41.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose, you get to move the picture frames in Kid's house by 2 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:48.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... If we lose, Captain Maka will go on a one-day date with her Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second. I don't understand the meaning of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the captain, Black Star? You want to be the captain, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:01.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! But I feel bad because I forced you to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:05.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's painful, you can have the position of captain! I'm already in tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get conscientious at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing the captain's cap, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:15.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I want to be the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then switch with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:20.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Soul, the opponent, pass the ball to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:25.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:26.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why did he throw it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Patty! Captain Maka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Defend the zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:35.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a zone? Teach me the rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it start? Stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:49.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no chance I'd find a marriage partner in a place with only kids around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids are students from Shibusen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And from tomorrow onwards they will be your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka fouled. Double dribble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's a double dribble?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds sort of cool though...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:21.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Though I don't have a lover, I'll work one more time before I get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it's kind of on short notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...but until I find an apartment, can I stay at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:32.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay with me, but I don't know if you'll be cut up or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm trusting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:40.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's about Stein-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he already noticed it himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he's in the process of being controlled by madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:58.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie-chan's soul wavelength should have a positive effect on Stein's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Spirit-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}will you help me keep an eye on Stein-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:06.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Spirit-kun, will you help me keep an eye on Stein-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:15.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when, you'll always be the Kouhai I have to look after, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Spirit-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass it here! Pass it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those guys doing? Even though they were told to say at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.77,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great that the kids are taking it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that they're taking it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that abnormal experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:42.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...they are doing what they can to return to their normal, everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Game set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,20 to 4. It's Maka's team's defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even until the very end, I couldn't understand the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pretend there was no penalty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.33,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Penalty game! {\alpha&HFF&}Penalty game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.83,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Penalty game! Penalty game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Penalty game! {\alpha&HFF&}Penalty game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Penalty game! Penalty game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.30,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Penalty game! {\alpha&HFF&}Penalty game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.30,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Penalty game! Penalty game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:07.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the underground battle, I don't think it will affect their normal daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have a normal daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Maka, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... Well, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This Sunday, do you want to... {\alpha&HFF&}go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This Sunday, do you want to... go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:38.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought I was going to be relocated somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, strawberry or banana, which is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Papa, which one suits me more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:46.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Papa. It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:52.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I never expected such an abnormal day to jump on me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:02.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Papa? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:07.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm just too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here. I'll get the stomach medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'm fine!
